{"tid":410954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中甲聯賽 雲南vs浙江，半場休息休息室停電，浙江球員被數十黑衣人暴打","createTime":"2017-09-23T11:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T14:42:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbacde0618f00d5b8c5a3b64f68b2f6d63a35190","tid":410954,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"毅騰俱樂部官方微博：<br />\n「突發！中甲聯賽第27輪浙江毅騰輕紡城客場挑戰雲南麗江的比賽進行到中場休息時間，毅騰休息室附近突然全部斷電，所有燈光熄滅，隨即數十名安保人員（特勤）不明原因<span style=\"color: red;\">手持警棍毆打多名毅騰球員</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">還將上半場毅騰進球功臣艾爾帕提-迪力夏提打傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n在如此惡劣的安保情況下，毅騰球員的生命安全無法得到保障，因此下半場比賽無法正常進行，現在多方正在協商中。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oL3iRqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoL3iRqJ.jpg&h=cd33ef88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrDYrNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrrDYrNY.jpg&h=d5bd5b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/peUbtn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpeUbtn0.jpg&h=211a1bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyyQgDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJyyQgDg.jpg&h=5e50e9af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5d76df32d45083d838179a665bb67b51336e457","tid":410954,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55750f6a1ce813d8c63decf3e13cd726d3c3f375","tid":410954,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3f891f7bef382ee9a360803281910e7541180ed","tid":410954,"uid":2419,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入左波都打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl